longBusinessSummary: The Warehouse Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the retail of general merchandise and apparel in New Zealand. The company also sells stationery products, technology and appliance products, and outdoor and sporting equipment. It operates 90 The Warehouse stores, 70 Warehouse Stationery stores, 71 Noel Leeming stores, and 21 Torpedo7 stores, as well as online stores. In addition, it is involved in the provision of property and investment services. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Auckland, New Zealand.
